c: 12
v: 30
t: "woo xaagi magaalah agabu yoofeeh usun kaat walaleenih:qaziiz (masri baaxok abbâ gubaytuh yan num kinnuk) barra assacakkuk:is isi awka isi nafsi fan dalwah secta, nummah is kaah abte kacni tet lubbik siba yoofe, diggah nanu is tamahat asse waqdi baxxaqqa itta makoh addat tet nable iyyen"